attack%20of%20this%20scale%20likely%20required%20months%20of%20planning%2C%20an%20arms%20expert%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20attack%20also%20shows%20a%20lack%20of%20oversight%20of%20global%20supply%20chains%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tuesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-backed-hezbollah-members-hurt-after-pagers-just-weirdly-exploded-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattack%20in%20Lebanon%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20hundreds%20of%20pagers%20used%20by%20the%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20simultaneously%20detonated%2C%20points%20to%20a%20highly%20sophisticated%20operation%20that%20likely%20required%20months%20of%20planning%20and%20an%20infiltration%20of%20a%20global%20supply%20chain%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%202%2C800%20people%20were%20injured%20and%2012%20killed%2C%20The%20Associated%20Press%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20Lebanese%20Health%20Ministry.%20The%20pagers%20exploded%20in%20Lebanon%20around%20Tuesday%20late%20afternoon.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20more%20limited%20attack%20involving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-devices-explode-in-lebanon-after-deadly-hezbollah-pager-blasts-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalkie-talkies%20and%20solar%20equipment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20exploded%20injured%20hundreds%20more%20and%20killed%20at%20least%2020%20people%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Flebanon-israel-exploding-pagers-hezbollah-syria-ce6af3c2e6de0a0dddfae48634278288%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAP%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20cited%20the%20Lebanese%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20not%20commented%20or%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack.%20US%20and%20other%20officials%20who%20were%20briefed%20on%20the%20operation%20and%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F17%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-hezbollah-pagers-explosives.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20Israel%20was%20behind%20the%20attack%20and%20infiltrated%20a%20batch%20of%20Taiwanese-branded%20pagers%20in%20order%20to%20plant%20explosives%20inside%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20and%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attack%20of%20this%20size%20requires%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20technical%20capabilities%20involving%20intelligence%20gathering%20and%20months%20of%20planning%2C%20a%20national%20security%20expert%20and%20arms%20expert%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20this%20operation%20suggests%20a%20complex%20supply-chain%20attack%20executed%20by%20a%20state%20actor%2C%26quot%3B%20N.R.%20Jenzen-Jones%2C%20a%20director%20at%20the%20Armament%20Research%20Services%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20would%20have%20required%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20terms%20of%20manpower%20and%20other%20resources%2C%20and%20likely%20months%20of%20planning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20Israel%20was%20indeed%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20as%20US%20officials%20have%20said%2C%20then%20it%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise%20from%20a%20country%20that%20has%20already%20proven%20its%20technical%20prowess%2C%20Sean%20McFate%2C%20a%20national%20security%20and%20foreign%20policy%20expert%20at%20Syracuse%20University's%20Maxwell%20School%20of%20Citizenship%20%26amp%3B%20Public%20Affairs%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20a%20very%20tech-savvy%20state%20with%20its%20own%20'Wadi%20Valley%2C'%20as%20they%20put%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20McFate%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupply-chain%20experts%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20attack%20showcases%20how%20vulnerabilities%20in%20global%20supply%20chains%20are%20often%20overlooked%20and%20can%20be%20exploited%20in%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20explosives%20were%20implanted%20in%20the%20pagers%20before%20reaching%20Hezbollah%20shows%20the%20challenges%20of%20securing%20electronics%20sourcing%2C%20especially%20with%20international%20shipments%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Khachatryan%2C%20CEO%20of%20Freight%20Right%20Global%20Logistics%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImages%20online%20appear%20to%20show%20that%20the%20pagers%20in%20the%20attack%20had%20branding%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhezbollahs-exploding-pagers-bought-taiwanese-company-denied-israel-explosive-material-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGold%20Apollo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20company%20based%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Ftaiwan-firm-denies-making-pagers-used-lebanon-explosions-rcna171594%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20company%20told%20the%20outlet%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20a%20Hungary-based%20entity%20called%20BAC%20Consulting%20was%20authorized%20to%20use%20Gold%20Apollo's%20branding%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bdesign%20and%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20prodcuts%20are%20entirely%20handled%20by%20BAC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECristiana%20B%C3%A1rsony-Arcidiacono%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20BAC%2C%20denied%20making%20the%20pagers%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20NBC%20News%20and%20said%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bjust%20the%20intermediate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20Apollo%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20Business%20Insider%20was%20not%20able%20to%20reach%20BAC%20Consulting%20for%20comment.%20The%20company's%20website%20appeared%20to%20be%20down%20as%20of%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenzen-Jones%20said%20that%20while%20supply%20chain%20attacks%20are%20often%20thought%20of%20in%20th