20How%20do%20we%20become%20household%20names%3F'%20We%20sat%20down%20and%20thought%20'I%20really%20need%20to%20plan%20this%20out.%20This%20can't%20happen%20by%20chance'%2C%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20said%20during%20the%20chat%20with%20head%20coach%20Gambhir%20in%20an%20interview%20arranged%20by%20the%20BCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20being%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20responsibility%2C%20Kohli%20decided%20to%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion.%20The%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20started%20thinking%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20where%20Indian%20cricket%20has%20to%20be%20in%207%20years'%20time%2C%20the%20solutions%20came.%20We%20need%20a%20group%20of%20fast%20bowlers.%20We%20need%20batters%20who%20can%20bat%20long.%20We%20need%20to%20give%20ownership%20to%20five%20batters%20and%20a%20keeper%20to%20get%20us%20350-400.%20We%20can't%20have%20a%20seventh%20option.%20I%20remember%20the%20challenge%20excited%20me.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20'Oh%20my%20god!%20I%20don't%20want%20any%20part%20in%20this'.%20And%20that's%20when%20I%20was%20like%20I%20am%20all%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20also%20found%20comfort%20in%20Gambhir's%20words%20as%20the%20India%20head%20coach%20lauded%20him%20for%20leading%20the%20troops%20valiantly%20despite%20being%20a%20young%2025-year-old%20batter%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20understand%20what%20you%20might%20have%20gone%20through.%20A%2024-25%20year-old%20boy%20taking%20up%20Test%20captaincy%20and%20then%20what%20you%20did%20brilliantly%20was%20that%20you%20had%20a%20really%20strong%20bowling%20unit.%20Test%20matches%20are%20won%20by%20taking%2020%20wickets.%20Till%20the%20time%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20strong%20bowling%20line-up%2C%20you%20won't%20%5Bwin%5D.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20made%20you%20the%20most%20successful%20Test%20captain%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gambhir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCredit%20has%20to%20go%20to%20you%20because%20as%20a%20batter%20it%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20have%20a%20strong%206-7%20batters%20putting%20runs%20on%20the%20board%20but%20the%20way%20you%20identified%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20attitude%20which%20you%20brought%20on%20the%20field%20from%20fast%20bowlers.%20Imagine%20having%20people%20like%20Shami%2C%20Bumrah%2C%20Ishant%2C%20Umesh%20and%20then%20winning%20overseas.%20I%20remember%20you%20playing%20that%20knock%20in%20Adelaide.%20We%20were%20chasing%20400%3B%20it%20was%20your%20first%20game%20as%20captain%2C%20and%20you%20still%20wanted%20to%20win%20that%20Test%20match.%20That%20is%20the%20mindset%2C%20that%20is%20the%20culture%20we%20want%20to%20bring%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726710600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhuodttl8_virat-kohli-and-gautam-gambhir-during-an-interview_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-opens-up-on-ms-dhoni-exit-challenge-gautam-gambhir-gives-priceless-response-6592899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20gave%20Virat%20Kohli%20the%20praise%20he%20deserved%20after%20the%20latter%20brought%20up%20the%20topic%20of%20MS%20Dhoni's%20exit%20as%20India's%20Test%20captain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-opens-up-on-ms-dhoni-exit-challenge-gautam-gambhir-gives-priceless-response-6592899%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Student%20Oscars%202024%3A%202%20Indian%20Filmmakers%20Triumph%20At%20Prestigious%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20Indian%20students%20have%20been%20honoured%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Student%20Academy%20Awards.%20The%20Academy%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20Arts%20and%20Sciences%20received%202%2C683%20entries%20from%20738%20colleges%20and%