eign%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Canada%20sees%20a%20spike%20in%20the%20number%20of%20refugee%20claimants%2C%20the%20government%20said%20Wednesday%20it%20planned%20to%20review%20measures%20to%20strengthen%20visa%20integrity%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Breviewing%20visa%20decision-making%20so%20that%20our%20highly%20trained%20officers%20have%20the%20right%20tools%20to%20detect%20fraud%20and%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20non-genuine%20visitors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20not%20everyone%20who%20wants%20to%20come%20to%20Canada%20will%20be%20able%20to%E2%80%94just%20like%20not%20everyone%20who%20wants%20to%20stay%20in%20Canada%20will%20be%20able%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Immigration%20Minister%20Marc%20Miller%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20already%20pledged%20to%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20temporary%20residents%20to%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%20It%20was%206.8%25%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMigrants%20have%20been%20blamed%20for%20societal%20problems%20including%20a%20lack%20of%20affordable%20housing%20and%20ramped-up%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20even%20as%20post-pandemic%20inflation%20slowed%20to%20the%20Bank%20of%20Canada's%20target%20of%202%25%20annually%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmigrant%20advocates%20and%20some%20economists%20argue%20the%20link%20between%20migrants%20and%20economic%20malaise%20is%20an%20oversimplification%2C%20and%20that%20vulnerable%20newcomers%20cannot%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20complex%20economic%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolls%20have%20shown%20a%20growing%20slice%20of%20the%20public%20thinks%20Canada%20is%20bringing%20in%20too%20many%20immigrants%2C%20and%20anti-migrant%20rhetoric%20and%20attacks%20have%20risen%20in%20Canada%2C%20once%20renowned%20for%20its%20welcoming%20stance%20toward%20newcomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20after%20years%20of%20increasing%20Canada's%20ranks%20of%20temporary%20residents%2C%20its%20federal%20government%20is%20seeking%20to%20pull%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20government%20placed%20a%20two-year%20cap%20on%20international%20students%2C%20whose%20approvals%20are%20projected%20to%20decrease%20by%20almost%20half%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20government%20walked%20back%202022%20expansions%20to%20the%20temporary%20foreign%20worker%20program.%20In%20some%20sectors%2C%20it%20reduced%20the%20maximum%20share%20of%20any%20employer's%20workforce%20that%20can%20be%20made%20up%20of%20low-wage%2C%20temporary%20foreign%20workers.%20It%20also%20ended%2C%20in%20some%20sectors%2C%20low-wage%20temporary%20foreign%20workers%20in%20communities%20with%20high%20unemployment%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726705380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F5segqcpc_justin-trudeau-reuters_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-to-further-cut-permits-for-international-students-foreign-workers-6598075%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20is%20further%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20study%20permits%20it%20will%20grant%20to%20foreign%20students%20and%20tightening%20eligibility%20for%20work%20permits%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20number%20of%20temporary%20residents%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20government%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-to-further-cut-permits-for-international-students-foreign-workers-6598075%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iranian%20hackers%20tried%20to%20send%20stolen%20Trump%20data%20to%20Biden%20associates%3A%20FBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%2