led%20beaches%2C%20beautiful%20views%2C%20and%20delicious%20food.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWaiheke%20Island%2C%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20is%20known%20to%20attract%20a%20wealthy%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Vogue%20journalist%20Amy%20Louise%20Bailey%20coined%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.com%2Farticle%2Fguide-to-waiheke-island-new-zealand%5C%22%3EHamptons%20of%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bescape%20that%20is%20high-end%20but%20low-key.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20eager%20to%20see%20if%20Waiheke%20lived%20up%20to%20its%20Hamptons%20reputation%2C%20so%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Auckland%20in%202022%2C%20I%20planned%20a%20two-night%20getaway%20to%20the%20island.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20I%20discovered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOff%20the%20coast%20of%20New%20Zealand's%20capital%20is%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20a%2036-square-mile%20island%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20country's%20wealthiest%20residents%20and%20vacationers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bird's%20eye%20view%20of%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F637648f21f38cc0012877fdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EFiona%20Ritchie%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20located%20in%20the%20Hauraki%20Gulf%20and%20has%20about%2010%2C000%20permanent%20residents.%20Many%20of%20those%20residents%20have%20familiar%20names%20and%20impressive%20titles%2C%20including%20New%20Zealand's%20richest%20man%2C%20Graeme%20Hart%2C%20and%20former%20All%20Blacks%20rugby%20coach%20Sir%20Graham%20Henry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20permanent%20residents%2C%20Waiheke%20Island%20is%20also%20considered%20a%20vacation%20hot%20spot.%20About%203%2C500%20people%20own%20vacation%20homes%20on%20the%20island%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mansionglobal.com%2Farticles%2Fa-ferry-commute-from-auckland-waiheke-island-offers-sun-sand-and-wine-228186%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMansion%20Global%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20rich%20and%20famous%20flock%20to%20those%20vacation%20homes%20to%20explore%20the%20island's%20wineries%2C%20pristine%20beaches%2C%20and%20dramatic%20landscapes.%20Waiheke%20has%20hosted%20everyone%20from%20Bill%20Gates%20to%20Madonna%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202022%2C%20I%20traveled%20to%20Waiheke%20to%20see%20what%20exactly%20entices%20affluent%20vacationers%20and%20residents%20to%20the%20island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20of%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20from%20a%20ferry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6375521c09495900110e90da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20from%20a%20ferry.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20rich%20vacationers%20often%20take%20private%20jets%20and%20boats%20to%20the%20island%2C%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20me.%20Instead%2C%20I%20joined%20residents%20and%20visitors%20on%20a%2040-minute%20ferry%20ride%20from%20Auckland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ferry%20was%20my%20first%20indicator%20that%20the%20island%20is%20a%20place%20for%20the%20wealthy.%20My%20round-trip%20ticket%20on%20the%20Fullers360%20ferry%20cost%20%2450%2C%20and%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nzherald.co.nz%2Fnz%2Fcost-of-living-pushing-waiheke-locals-off-the-island%2FZ655FBU5Q5NXWD7IS2YZ77MN3M%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Zealand%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20public%20ferries%20in%20the%20world%20at%20the%20time%2C%20costing%20locals%20%24250%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20the%20ferry%20departed%20from%20Auckland%2C%20the%20city's%20harbor%20and%20Sky%20Tower%20faded%20into%20the%20distance.%20A%20little%20over%20half%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20a%20lush%2C%20green%20island%20speckled%20with%20homes%20came%20into%20view.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ferry%20station%20in%20the%20Waiheke%20Island%20terminal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6375526b2d22e7001161f6dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20ferry%20station%20in%20the%20Waiheke%20Island%20terminal.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20disembarked%20from%20the%20ferry%20and%20set%20out%20to%20explore%20Waiheke.%20Although%20the%20island%20is%2036%20square%20miles%2C%20the%20western%20half%20is%20more%20developed%2C%20with%20a%20concentration%20of%20wineries%20and%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20first%20stop%20was%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard%2C%20where%20I%20planned%20to%20do%20what%20Vogue%20says%20locals%2C%20tourists%2C%20and%20wealthy%20visitors%20do%20%E2%80%94%20sip%20wine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20to%20the%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard%20and%20Restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F637554392d22e7001161f77f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20the%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard%20and%20Restaurant.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWaiheke%20Island%20is%20home%20to%20more%20than%2030%20wineries%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20the%20region's%20micro-climate%2C%20Syrah%20and%20Cabernet%20blends%20thrive%20in%20Waiheke's%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMudbrick%20W