20boutique%20hotels%2C%20but%20most%20visitors%20book%20vacation%20homes%20for%20their%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDotted%20along%20the%20coast%20are%20these%20rental%20properties%2C%20many%20of%20which%20cost%20millions%20of%20dollars.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realestate.co.nz%2Finsights%2Fauckland%2Fwaiheke-island%2Fwaiheke-island%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERealestate.co.nz%3C%2Fa%3E%20reports%20that%20the%20island's%20median%20asking%20price%20for%20a%20home%20was%20%242.5%20million%20this%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20real-estate%20prices%20have%20fluctuated%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Waiheke%20is%20one%20of%20the%20places%20where%20homes%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stuff.co.nz%2Flife-style%2Fhomed%2Freal-estate%2F131306809%2Fthe-towns-where-house-prices-have-doubled-over-the-last-10-years%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20doubled%20in%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20headed%20first%20to%20Cable%20Bay%20Lane%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20ritzy%20vacation%20properties%20like%20Fossil%20Cove%2C%20the%20property%20where%20Lady%20Gaga%20stayed%20when%20she%20visited%20the%20island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20helicopter%20at%20a%20vineyard%20on%20Waiheke%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63764f4a1f38cc00128781bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20helicopter%20at%20a%20vineyard%20on%20Waiheke%20Island.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20T%20Hall%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Fossil%20Cove%20costs%20more%20than%20%246%2C000%20a%20night%20with%20a%20minimum%207-night%20stay.%20The%20stay%20includes%20daily%20butler%20service%2C%20Champagne%2C%20and%20transfers%20from%20the%20ferry%20wharf%20or%20helipad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20drove%20down%20Cable%20Bay%20Lane%20searching%20for%20other%20modern