0I%20hike%20around%20Owhanake%20Bay.%20The%20cliffs%20there%2C%20he%20said%2C%20allow%20a%20better%20view%20of%20Waiheke's%20multimillion-dollar%20mansions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20hopped%20in%20my%20car%20and%20headed%20to%20Owhanake%20Bay.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20parking%20lot%20at%20Owhanake%20Bay.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63754ef309495900110e8fba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20parking%20lot%20at%20Owhanake%20Bay%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20climbed%20up%20and%20through%20a%20forested%20area%2C%20the%20hiking%20trail%20led%20me%20to%20a%20freshly%20paved%20road%20that%20had%20a%20scattering%20of%20large%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThanks%20to%20the%20hike's%20high%20elevation%2C%20I%20spotted%20mansions%20Waiheke's%20rich%20and%20famous%20own.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mansion%20along%20the%20hike.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63754e172d22e7001161f55f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mansion%20along%20the%20hike.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20visitor%2C%20it%20was%20enticing%20to%20see%20these%20pricey%20homes%2C%20but%20after%20speaking%20with%20locals%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20these%20properties%2C%20over-tourism%2C%20and%20visitors%20like%20me%20have%20pushed%20permanent%20residents%20off%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Waiheke%20has%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20homelessness%20per%20capita%20in%20the%20Auckland%20region%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.co.nz%2F2024%2F08%2F17%2Ftourists-push-locals-out-of-waiheke-islan