ning%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63754c242d22e7001161f4b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20Waiheke's%20main%20shopping%20and%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20to%20see%20designer%20stores%2C%20luxe%20window%20displays%2C%20and%20fine%20dining.%20Instead%2C%20the%20area%20was%20surprisingly%20quaint.%20Restaurants%20served%20everything%20from%20burgers%20to%20grand%20seafood%20dinners%2C%20and%20there%20wasn't%20a%20designer%20store%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20laid-back%20charm%20was%20across%20the%20whole%20island.%20When%20I%20first%20arrived%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20I%20feared%20I%20might%20feel%20out%20of%20place.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20main%20street%20of%20Waiheke%20Island%20in%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6375564f09fde90011909211%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20main%20street%20of%20Waiheke%20Island%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20far%20from%20able%20to%20distinguish%20between%20a%20%2420%20and%20%24200%20bottle%20of%20wine%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20one%20to%20insist%20on%20turn-down%20service%20in%20my%20hotel%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20during%20two%20days%20on%20the%20island%2C%20I%20discovered%20much%20more%20than%20hot%20tubs%2C%20six-car%20garages%2C%20and%20helipads.%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20wealthy%20traveler%20to%20enjoy%20Waiheke%20Island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20vineyard%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e1986ce1179200195ea0b