%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ffed-rate-cut-climate_n_66eadef3e4b00648275b7556%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%201st%20Since%202020%2C%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20Cuts%20Interest%20Rate%20By%2050%20Basis%20Point%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20cut%20its%20key%20lending%20rate%20by%20half%20a%20percentage-point%20Wednesday%20in%20its%20first%20reduction%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20sharply%20lowering%20borrowing%20costs%20shortly%20before%20November's%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed's%20decision%20will%20affect%20the%20rates%20at%20which%20commercial%20banks%20lend%20to%20consumers%20and%20businesses%2C%20bringing%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20borrowing%20on%20everything%20from%20mortgages%20to%20credit%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20will%20likely%20be%20well-received%20by%20Democratic%20candidate%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20has%20looked%20to%20highlight%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20economic%20record%20in%20her%20race%20against%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolicymakers%20voted%2011-to-1%20in%20favor%20of%20lowering%20the%20US%20central%20bank's%20benchmark%20rate%20to%20between%204.75%20percent%20and%205.00%20percent%2C%20the%20Fed%20announced%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20holdout%20was%20Fed%20governor%20Michelle%20Bowman%2C%20who%20supported%20a%20more%20conventional%20quarter-point%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFed%20'gained%20greater%20confidence'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20said%20its%20rate-setting%20committee%20%26quot%3Bhas%20gained%20greater%20confidence%20that%20inflation%20is%20moving%20sustainably%20toward%202%20percent%2C%20and%20judges%20that%20the%20risks%20to%20achieving%20its%20employment%20and%20inflation%20goals%20are%20roughly%20in%20balance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20a%20dual%20mandate%20from%20Congress%20to%20act%20independently%20to%20tackle%20both%20inflation%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20were%20expecting%20the%20Fed%20to%20cut%20rates%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20inflation%20eases%20toward%20the%20bank's%20long-term%20target%20of%20two%20percent%2C%20and%20the%20labor%20market%20continues%20to%20cool%20in%20the%20surprisingly%20resilient%20post-Covid%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20were%20highly%20uncertain%20about%20the%20size%20of%20the%20move%2C%20with%20some%20anticipating%20a%20small%20cut%20of%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20percentage%20point%2C%20and%20others%20predicting%20the%20more%20significant%20half-point%20cut%2C%20which%20carries%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20reigniting%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20updated%20economic%20forecasts%20published%20alongside%20the%20Fed's%20rate%20decision%2C%20policymakers'%20median%20forecasts%20pointed%20to%20an%20unemployment%20rate%20of%204.4%20percent%2C%20on%20average%2C%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%204.0%20percent%20in%20the%20last%20update%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20penciled%20in%20an%20annual%20headline%20inflation%20rate%20of%202.3%20percent%2C%20slightly%20lower%20than%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20cut%20more%20sharply%20to%20begin%20with%20caught%20some%20analysts%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20base%20case%20the%20Fed%20cuts%2025bp%20(basis%20points)%20but%20signals%20100bp%20of%20cuts%20this%20year%20with%20the%20median%202024%20'dot'%26quot%3B%2C%20economists%20at%20Citi%20wrote%20in%20an%20investor%20note%20published%20ahead%20of%20the%20rate%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElection%20stakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed's%20mandate%20gives%20it%20the%20independence%20to%20set%20monetary%20policy%20solely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20economic%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20decision%20will%20likely%20have%20political%20ramifications%2C%20given%20the%20importance%20of%20inflation%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20to%20US%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmericans%20have%20consistently%20said%20both%20are%20a%20top%20concern%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20Fed%20Chair%20Powell%2C%20who%20he%20first%20appointed%20to%20run%20the%20Fed%2C%20and%20has%20suggested%20that%20its%20decisions%20are%20political%20--%20accusations%20the%20US%20central%20bank%20has%20strongly%20refuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726683840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fud2ua6_us-federal-reserve-_625x300_11_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-first-cut-since-covid-pandemic-us-federal-reserve-reduces-interest-rates-by-50-basis-points-6596876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20cut%20its%20key%20lending%20rate%20by%20half%20a%20percentage-point%20Wednesday%20in%20its%20first%20reduction%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20sharply%20lowering%20borrowing%20costs%20shortly%20before%20November's%20presidential%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-first-cut-since-covid-pandemic-us-federal-reserve-reduces-interest-rates-by-50-basis-points-6596876%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Polish%20army%20in%20race%20to%20beat%20rising%20floodwater%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726683540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F09%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-wroclaw-poland-flooding_6689612.jpg%3F20240918193518%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpolish-army-in-race-to-beat-rising-floodwater-as-country-declares-a-disaster-13217