on%20Tuesday.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20dead%20in%20Tuesday's%20explosions%20has%20risen%20to%2012%2C%20including%20two%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20attacks%20have%20raised%20Hezbolah's%20tensions%20with%20Israel%20-%20which%20it%20has%20blamed%20for%20the%20pager%20explosions%20-%20that%20were%20already%20high%20because%20of%20Tel%20Aviv's%20war%20with%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20group%20said%20it%20had%20used%20rockets%20to%20attack%20Israeli%20artillery%20positions%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20coordinated%20targeting%20of%20communication%20devices%20used%20by%20Hezbollah%20is%20being%20widely%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20throw%20the%20group%20in%20disarray%20and%20a%20way%20of%20demonstrating%20to%20its%20members%20that%20the%20attackers%20can%20get%20at%20them%20in%20ways%20they%20least%20expect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20senior%20Lebanese%20security%20source%20and%20another%20person%20in%20the%20know%20told%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20that%20Israel's%20spy%20agency%20Mossad%2C%20which%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20carrying%20out%20sophisticated%20operations%20on%20foreign%20soil%2C%20planted%20explosives%20inside%20pagers%20imported%20by%20Hezbollah%20months%20before%20they%20went%20off%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20senior%20Lebanese%20security%20source%20told%20Reuters%20the%20group%20had%20ordered%205%2C000%20pagers%20made%20by%20Taiwan-based%20Gold%20Apollo%20and%20another%20source%20said%20three%20grams%20of%20explosives%20had%20been%20hidden%20in%20each%20of%20the%20ordered%20devices%2C%20which%20had%20gone%20undetected%20for%20months.%20Gold%20Apollo%20said%20the%20devices%20were%20made%20under%20licence%20by%20a%20company%20called%20BAC%2C%20based%20in%20Hungary.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIran's%20state%20media%20had%20reported%20that%20its%20Ambassador%20to%20Lebanon%2C%20Mojtaba%20Amani%2C%20was%20also%20wounded%20in%20Tuesday's%20explosions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20walkie-talkies%20which%20exploded%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20source%20told%20Reuters%2C%20were%20purchased%20by%20Hezbollah%20five%20months%20ago%2C%20around%20the%20same%20time%20that%20the%20pagers%20were%20bought.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnited%20Nations%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20civilian%20objects%20should%20not%20be%20weaponised.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20very%20important%20that%20there%20is%20an%20effective%20control%20of%20civilian%20objects%2C%20not%20to%20weaponise%20civilian%20objects...%20that%20should%20be%20a%20rule%20that%20governments%20should%2C%20be%20able%20to%20implement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Guterres%20also%20warned%20of%20a%20risk%20of%20serious%20escalation.%20%26quot%3BAs%20important%20as%20the%20event%20in%20itself%2C%20is%20the%20indication%20that%20this%20event%20confirms%20that%20there%20is%20a%20serious%20risk%20of%20a%20dramatic%20escalation%20in%20Lebanon%20--%20and%20everything%20must%20be%20done%20to%20avoid%20the%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726682820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmfsk2khg_lebanon-walkie-talkie-blasts_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpagers-then-walkie-talkies-how-devices-were-weaponised-against-hezbollah-6596167%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twin%20attacks%20using%20communication%20devices%2C%20suspected%20to%20have%20an%20Israeli%20hand%2C%20have%20struck%20fear%20in%20the%20ranks%20of%20Hezbollah%2C%20the%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%20based%20in%20Lebanon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpagers-then-walkie-talkies-how-devices-were-weaponised-against-hezbollah-6596167%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengal%20Floods%20Man-Made%20Disaster%2C%20Says%20Mamata%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20rushed%20to%20flood-hit%20areas%20in%20Hooghly%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20South%20Bengal%20today%2C%20which%20have%20been%20massively%20affected%20by%20the%20release%20of%20water%20from%20dams%20upstream%20in%20Jharkhand.%20Accusing%20the%20Damodar%20Valley%20Corporation%20of%20being%20responsible%20for%20the%20situation%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Central%20government's%20DVC%20and%20Jharkhand's%20Tenughat%20and%20Panchet%2C%20they%20have%20saved%20their%20own%20state%20and%20released%20water%20into%20Bengal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhs%20of%20people%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20floods%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20flow%20and%20speed%20of%20the%20water.%20Everything%20will%20go%20underwater%20at%20any%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20districts%20in%20Bengal%20--%20Howrah%2C%20Hooghly%2C%20Birbhum%2C%20West%20Midnapore%2C%20East%20Midnapore%2C%20Jhargram%2C%20Bankura%2C%20Purulia%2C%20West%20Burdwan%2C%20and%20East%20Burdwan%20--%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20the%20affected%20areas%20in%20West%20Midnapore%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deep%20depression%20over%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%20has%20led%20to%20heavy%20rains%20in%20southern%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20over%20the%20weekend%20and%20on%20Monday.%20Jharkhand%20also%20saw%20heavy%20rains%20on%20Monday%20leading%20to%20release%20of%20excess%20water%20from%20dams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DVC%20or%20Damodar%20Valley%20Corporation%20released%2090%2C000%20cusecs%20of%20water%20on%20Monday%20night%20and%202.1%20lakh%20cusecs%20on%20Tuesday.%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20spoken%20to%20her%20Jharkhand%20counterpart%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20kind%20of%20water%20discharge%20had%20never%20happened%20before.%20DVC%20has%20released%203.5%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water.%20I%20have%20talked%20with%20the%20DVC%20officials%20and%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister.%20But%20of%20no%20avail%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20district%20administrations%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20prepare%20flood%20shelters%20and%20stock%20adequate%20drinking%20water%2C%20medicines%2C%20and%20dry%20food.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFlood%20like%20situation%20may%20occur%20in%20the%20lower%20basin%20area%20of%20the%20Damodar%20valley%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains%20and%20release%20of%20excess%20water%20from%20dams%20and%20barrages...%20Senior%20officers%20have%20been%20posted%20in%20the%20districts%20to%20handle%20the%20situation...%20People%20from%20low%20lying%20areas%20have%20been%20ordered%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alapan%20Bandopadhyay%2C%20advisor%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20hit%20out%20at%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20described%20her%20visit%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%20as%20a%20PR%20stunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCM%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20your%20ploy%20and%20strategy%20to%20shift%20blame%20is%20getting%20old%20and%20repetitive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20her%20of%20blaming%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20then%20DVC%20responsible%20for%20floods%20in%20Bengal%20every%20time%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20that%20you%20and%20your%20Irrigation%20%26amp%3B%20Waterways%20Department%20are%20an%20utter%20failure%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20you%20take%20any%20preventive%20or%20precautionary%20measures%20before%20the%20monsoons%20nor%20you%20have%20taken%20any%20steps%20to%20boost%20the%20infrastructure%20in%20order%20to%20tackle%20the%20annual%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726682580000%2C%22visual%2