2summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113467261.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAn%20explosion%20at%20an%20under-construction%20gas%20field%20in%20Uzbekistan%20killed%20at%20least%20two%20people%20and%20injured%20others.%20Occurring%20near%20Baysun%2C%20this%20follows%20a%20previous%20incident%20releasing%20hydrogen%20sulphide%20gas.%20Authorities%20closed%20schools%20and%20evacuated%20workers.%20Discovered%20during%20the%20Soviet%20era%2C%20the%20gas%20field%20is%20now%20being%20developed%20with%20foreign%20investment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-two-killed-in-gas-field-explosion-in-uzbekistan%2Farticleshow%2F113467261.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-two-killed-in-gas-field-explosion-in-uzbekistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F113467261.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-two-killed-in-gas-field-explosion-in-uzbekistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F113467261.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Panel%20On%20Simultaneous%20Polls%20Studied%20Process%20In%20Sweden%2C%20Germany%2C%20Japan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20high-level%20panel%20on%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20studied%20election%20processes%20in%20seven%20countries%20including%20South%20Africa%2C%20Sweden%20and%20Belgium%2C%20before%20recommending%20simultaneous%20polls%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20committee's%20report%20approved%20by%20Union%20Cabinet%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20countries%20where%20simultaneous%20elections%20are%20conducted%20are%20Germany%2C%20Japan%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20the%20Phillipines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20led%20by%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20had%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20in%20March%20recommending%20simultaneous%20elections%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20as%20the%20first%20step%20followed%20by%20synchronised%20local%20body%20polls%20within%20100%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20a%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20other%20countries%20was%20drawn%20while%20dealing%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20simultaneous%20elections.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20study%20and%20adopt%20the%20best%20international%20practices%20to%20ensure%20fairness%20and%20transparency%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20South%20Africa%2C%20voters%20cast%20their%20ballots%20for%20both%20the%20National%20Assembly%20and%20Provincial%20Legislatures%20simultaneously.%20However%2C%20municipal%20elections%20are%20held%20separately%20from%20provincial%20ones%20in%20a%20five-year%20cycle.%20On%20May%2029%2C%20South%20Africa%20will%20hold%20its%20general%20elections%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20National%20Assembly%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Provincial%20Legislature%20for%20each%20province%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20noted%20that%20Sweden%20follows%20the%20proportional%20electoral%20system%2C%20which%20means%20that%20political%20parties%20are%20assigned%20a%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20elected%20assembly%20based%20on%20their%20share%20of%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20system%20where%20elections%20for%20the%20Parliament%20(Riksdag)%2C%20County%20Councils%20and%20Municipal%20Councils%20all%20take%20place%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20These%20elections%20occur%20every%20four%20years%20on%20the%20second%20Sunday%20of%20September%20whereas%20elections%20to%20the%20municipal%20assemblies%20occur%20on%20the%20second%20Sunday%20of%20September%2C%20once%20every%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20C%20Kashyap%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%2C%20supported%20the%20German%20model%20of%20a%20constructive%20vote%20of%20no-confidence%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20procedure%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20chancellor%20made%20by%20the%20Bundestag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20also%20explained%20the%20process%20that%20is%20followed%20in%20Japan.%20In%20Japan%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20firstly%20appointed%20by%20the%20National%20Diet%20and%20thereafter%20accepted%20by%20the%20Emperor.%20He%20advocated%20adoption%20of%20a%20model%20similar%20to%20German%20or%20Japanese%20model.%20This%2C%20in%20his%20view%2C%20will%20also%20be%20beneficial%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%2C%202019%20Indonesia%20has%20been%20conducting%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20a%20system%20where%20the%20President%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20and%20members%20of%20both%20national%20and%20regional%20legislative%20bodies%20are%20elected%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoters%20cast%20a%20secret%20ballot%20and%20dip%20their%20fingers%20in%20indelible%20ink%20to%20prevent%20duplicate%20voting.%20Political%20parties%20need%204%20pc%20of%20votes%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20National%20Parliament.%20A%20presidential%20candidate%20needs%20more%20than%2050%20pc%20of%20votes%20cast%20overall%20and%20at%20least%2020%20pc%20of%20votes%20in%20more%20than%20half%20the%20country's%20provinces%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20February%2014%2C%202024%2C%20Indonesia%20successfully%20conducted%20simultaneous%20elections.%20It%20is%20being%20termed%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20single%20day%20elections%20since%20nearly%20200%20million%20people%20voted%20across%20all%20five%20levels%20--%20President%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Members%20of%20Regional%20Assemblies%20and%20Municipal%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E