they%20could%20insert%20explosive%20material%20within%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20declined%20to%20comment.%20The%20prime%20minister's%20office%20which%20has%20oversight%20of%20Mossad%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYossi%20Kuperwasser%2C%20a%20former%20military%20intelligence%20official%20and%20now%20research%20director%20at%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20and%20Security%20Forum%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20confirmation%20that%20the%20military%20intelligence%20unit%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%208200's%20members%20were%20some%20of%20the%20best%20and%20brightest%20personnel%20in%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20serving%20in%20a%20unit%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20Israel's%20defence%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenges%20they%20are%20facing%20are%20immense%2C%20very%20demanding%2C%20and%20we%20need%20the%20best%20people%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20-%20and%20its%20legion%20of%20young%2C%20hand-picked%20soldiers%20-%20develops%20and%20operates%20intelligence%20gathering%20tools%20and%20is%20often%20likened%20to%20the%20U.S.%20National%20Security%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20public%20statement%20about%20the%20unit's%20activities%2C%20the%20IDF%20said%20in%202018%20that%20it%20had%20helped%20to%20thwart%20an%20air%20attack%20by%20Islamic%20State%20on%20a%20Western%20country.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20it%20said%20the%20unit's%20operations%20ran%20from%20intelligence%20gathering%20and%20cyber%20defence%20to%20%26quot%3Btechnological%20attacks%20and%20strikes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Israel%20has%20never%20confirmed%20its%20involvement%2C%20Unit%208200%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20Stuxnet%20attack%20that%20disabled%20Iranian%20nuclear%20centrifuges%20as%20well%20as%20a%20series%20of%20other%20high-profile%20operations%20outside%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYOUNG%20RECRUITS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20is%20effectively%20Israel's%20early%20warning%20system%2C%20and%20like%20much%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20defence%20and%20security%20establishment%2C%20shouldered%20some%20of%20the%20blame%20for%20failing%20to%20detect%20Hamas'%20Oct.%207%20assault%20on%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20commander%20last%20week%20said%20he%20was%20stepping%20down.%20In%20his%20resignation%20letter%20carried%20by%20Israeli%20media%2C%20he%20said%20he%20hadn't%20fulfilled%20his%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20is%20famous%20for%20a%20work%20culture%20that%20emphasizes%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%20to%20tackle%20issues%20previously%20not%20encountered%20or%20imagined.%20This%20helped%20some%20graduates%20build%20Israel's%20high-tech%20sector%20and%20some%20of%20its%20biggest%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20a%20problem%20with%20software%20weakness%2C%20math%2C%20encryption%2C%20a%20problem%20hacking%20into%20something%20...%20you%20must%20be%20capable%20of%20doing%20it%20on%20your%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Avi%20Shua%2C%20a%20graduate%20of%208200%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%20co-found%20Orca%20Security%2C%20a%20cloud%20security%20unicorn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20has%20a%20high%20turnover%20rate%20of%20young%20recruits%20replacing%20veterans%2C%20said%20Kobi%20Samboursky%2C%20another%20former%208200%20member%20and%20Managing%20Partner%20at%20Glilot%20Capital%20Partners%2C%20an%20early-stage%20fund%20investing%20in%20cybersecurity%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20significant%20thing%20here%20is%20the%20'can-do'%20culture%2C%20where%20everything%20is%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Samboursky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%