%20was%20always%20fond%20of%20cooking%20food%20with%20what%20she%20harvested%20in%20her%20backyard.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20she%20was%20never%20able%20to%20commercialise%20the%20products.%20All%20her%20time%20went%20into%20looking%20after%20our%20two%20children%20and%20my%20parents.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20focus%20on%20starting%20the%20business%20only%20after%20my%20retirement.%20Now%20that%20my%20parents%20are%20no%20more%20and%20our%20children%20are%20settled%2C%20she%20has%20all%20the%20time%20to%20fulfil%20her%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20husband%20Tom%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20smiles%20as%20he%20fondly%20recalls%20how%20his%20wife%20was%20always%20his%20rock%20when%20he%20was%20still%20working.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20my%20retirement%2C%20I%20just%20offered%20her%20some%20support%20and%20she%20started%20doing%20this%20work.%20While%20I%20was%20in%20service%2C%20she%20was%20my%20backbone%2C%20and%20now%2C%20I%20try%20to%20be%20hers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Beena%20began%20her%20journey%20by%20undergoing%20training%20in%20beekeeping%20and%20the%20value%20addition%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20through%20various%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%20in%20Kumarakom.%20Following%20her%20training%2C%20she%20started%20processing%20honey%20and%20creating%20products%20like%20honey%20soaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20she%20refined%20her%20skills%20and%20learned%20to%20create%20a%20variety%20of%20innovative%20products%20from%20bananas%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20other%20fruits.%20Apart%20from%20her%20garden%2C%20Beena%20and%20her%20husband%20also%20manage%2060%20bee%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%20magic%3A%20Beena%20Tom%E2%80%99s%20speciality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20acres%20that%20make%20up%20Beena%E2%80%99s%20backyard%2C%20everything%20is%20organically%20grown.%20%E