it%20user%2C%20who%20resides%20in%20the%20UK%20asked%20his%20fellow%20NRIs%20the%20reasons%20for%20not%20returning%20to%20India.%C2%A0''We've%20seen%20threads%20where%20people%20have%20outlined%20what%20they%20miss%20about%20India%20when%20living%20abroad%20-%20conveniences%2C%20house%20help%2C%20family%2C%20festivals%2C%20cheaper%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20and%20more.%20These%20are%20true%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20So%20for%20those%20who've%20settled%20abroad%20-%20what's%20stopping%20you%20from%20returning%3F''%2C%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20then%20explained%20his%20reasons%20for%20not%20returning%20to%20India.%20He%20cited%C2%A0good%20infrastructure%2C%20work-life%20balance%2C%20a%20judgement-free%20society%2C%20and%20a%20low%20crime%20rate%20as%20his%20reasons%20for%20settling%20in%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAskIndia%2Fcomments%2F1fi0yx4%2Findians_abroad_whats_stopping_you_from_returning%2F%5C%22%3EIndians%20abroad%20-%20what's%20stopping%20you%20from%20returning%20to%20India%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2Fbeer-and-crisps%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2Fbeer-and-crisps%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAskIndia%2F%5C%22%3EAskIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20query%20has%20prompted%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20responses%2C%20with%20some%20users%20confessing%20that%20their%20sole%20motivation%20for%20staying%20abroad%20is%20financial%20gain.%20Some%20NRIs%20talked%20about%20the%20superior%20infrastructure%20in%20their%20adopted%20countries%2C%20highlighting%20issues%20in%20India%20such%20as%20inadequate%20public%20transportation%2C%20poor%20road%20conditions%2C%20and%20unreliable%20utilities.%20Others%20pointed%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20civic%20sense%20among%20Indians%2C%20contrasting%20it%20with