l%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGlaciers%20in%20the%20region%20have%20shrunk%20by%2040%25%20in%20area%20and%2025%25%20in%20volume%20since%20around%201650%20AD.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20reduces%20the%20glacier%20melt%20that%20replenishes%20groundwater.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20study%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20specific%20measurements%20of%20groundwater%20level%20decline%2C%20it%20states%20that%20these%20factors%20have%20led%20to%20an%20imbalance%20between%20water%20demand%20and%20supply%2C%20decline%20of%20shallow%20resources%2C%20reduction%20of%20natural%20discharge%2C%20drying%20of%20springs%2C%20and%20decline%20in%20water%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20immediate%20intervention%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20will%20continue%20to%20decline%20rapidly%20over%20the%20next%2020%E2%80%9330%20years.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20countdown%20we%20cannot%20ignore%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Chorol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20actionable%20solutions%20that%20the%20local%20government%2C%20administration%2C%20business%20owners%2C%20and%20residents%20can%20take%20to%20address%20the%20growing%20concern%20surrounding%20groundwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Stricter%20regulations%20for%20groundwater%20extraction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mandatory%20permits%20for%20groundwater%20extraction%3B%20metering%20of%20groundwater%20usage%3B%20pricing%20of%20groundwater%3B%20strict%20zoning%20regulations%3B%20establish%20clear%20guidelines%20on%20the%20minimum%20distance%20between%20borewells%20and%20septic%20tanks%3B%20hefty%20fines%20for%20businesses%20found%20dumping%20waste%20in%20water%20bodies%3B%20and%20regular%20mapping%20of%20groundwater%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Upgrading%20and%20improving%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20sewage%20management%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Establish%20a%20decentralised%20sewage%20treatment%20plan%20with%20small-scale%20treatment%20systems%3B%20install%20advanced%20septic%20systems%20and%20dry%20toilets%20and%20composting%20systems%3B%20upgrade%20existing%20STPs%20and%20construct%20new%20ones%20in%20areas%20not%20covered%20by%20sewage%20network%3B%20invest%20in%20advanced%20water%20treatment%20technologies%3B%20and%20establishing%20a%20regular%20water%20quality%20monitoring%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Tourism%20industry%20stepping%20up%20to%20the%20plate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Encourage%20hotels%2C%20guesthouses%2C%20and%20restaurants%20to%20install%20water-efficient%20fixtures%3B%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20greywater%20recycling%20systems%3B%20install%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%3B%20charge%20water%20conservation%20fees%20for%20tourists%20with%20proceeds%20going%20to%20local%20water%20management%20projects%3B%20and%20mandatory%20water%20audits%20for%20all%20hotels%20and%20guesthouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Leveraging%20traditional%20water%20management%20systems%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Promote%20traditional%20rotational%20water%20distribution%20system%20(%3Cem%3Ebandabas%3C%2Fem%3E)%3B%20implement%20indigenous%20engineering%20techniques%2C%20such%20as%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20intricate%20canal%20systems%20(%3Cem%3Ema-yur%2C%20yu-ra%3C%2Fem%3E)%3B%20develop%20and%20implement%20context-appropriate%20irrigation%20systems%20taking%20into%20account%20modernisation%20and%20climate%20change%3B%20and%20introduce%20traditional%20ceremonies%20related%20to%20water%20management%20to%20get%20buy-in%20for%20the%20conservation%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(In%20Part%202%2C%20we%20will%20further%20discuss%20actionable%20solutions%20and%20recommendations%20by%20experts%20to%20mitigate%20the%20extraction%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20and%20improve%20its%20quality.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%2C%20