0charging%20network%20operators.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20companies%2C%20particularly%20in%20public%20transportation%20and%20fleet%20management%2C%20have%20shown%20interest.%20We%20have%20received%20preliminary%20commitments%20and%20purchase%20orders%20from%20fleet%20operators%20and%20EV%20charging%20infrastructure%20developers%2C%20including%20local%20government%20initiatives%20for%20public%20charging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Plugzmart)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725976650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D365359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai-based%20Plugzmart%20secured%20ARAI%20certification%20for%20its%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%2C%20marking%20a%20key%20step%20in%20advancing%20India%E2%80%99s%20electric%20vehicle%20infrastructure.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20charger%E2%80%99s%20proprietary%20controller%20enhances%20compatibility%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20high-speed%20charging%20capabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Startup%20%E2%80%98Fulva%E2%80%99%2C%204%20Friends%20Take%2024%20Types%20of%20Kozhikoden%20Halwa%20to%20The%20World%3B%20Earn%20Rs%2084%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHamza%20Shaheem%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Kozhikode%2C%20recalls%20the%20very%20first%20time%20he%20was%20treated%20to%20a%20particular%20red%20sweet%20from%20a%20bakery%20near%20his%20home%20in%20Feroke.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20so%20good!%E2%80%9D%20he%20exclaims%20as%20he%20retrieves%20the%20memory%20from%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20others%2C%20all%20involving%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that